{
  "stem": "11723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because being a little four-year-old and stumbling over these dead bodies, it's just, I can't explain it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was horrifying, absolutely horrifying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We finally arrived a barn that belong to somebody's estate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the estate was in shambles, in ruins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The barn was standing and there was a lot of hay in there, so we slept there with the horses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No food, but at least we had a place to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And no heat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was just everybody slept in their clothing in the hay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then the next morning they decided that we have to split up to many groups because nobody's going to take in 100 children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So my group was the youngest children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we went with two adults.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I don't know where those two adults found two sleds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were pulling us on a sled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we hardly ever met anybody on the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were only dead people on the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Nobody went outside because there was fighting going on all around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And whenever they could, they pulled us on the sled, but except for Susie, my sister, we had to take turns walking because it was kind of heavy for the women.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the next day I remember that evening was coming and we had no place to stay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we found a bombed-out house, an apartment building, but there was one part of it that was intact and even had working stove, a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now mind you, not electric stove like I have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "A wood-burning stove on which you could cook.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there was no water and no food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we haven't eaten in some time now.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
